login_device_alert.text:
Hello!

We noticed a sign-in attempt from a new or unrecognized device.

Time: {time}
Device: {device}
IP address: {ip}

If this was you, you can continue signing in with the verification code. If this was not you, please change your PIN immediately.

sponsored.text:
Hello!

{inviterName} invited you to the room "{roomTitle}" and paid for one month of access.
Selected role: {roleLabel}

Join: {joinLink}

After the first month ends, you need to activate your own subscription from the Subscription page to continue using the platform.

If you did not expect this email, you can ignore it.

